    <article id="post-5868" class="post-5868 post type-post status-publish format-link has-post-thumbnail hentry category-others tag-the-process-of-filing-the-application-for-ldc post_format-post-format-link">
                <div class="index-post-thumbnail">
            <a href="https://neerajbhagat.com/blog/index.php/lower-tax-deduction-certificate-how-to-apply/">
                <img width="800" height="419" src="https://neerajbhagat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Add-a-heading-800x419.png" class="attachment-simpleasy-featured-image size-simpleasy-featured-image wp-post-image" alt="Lower Tax Deduction Certificate: How to Apply" srcset="https://neerajbhagat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Add-a-heading-800x419.png 800w, https://neerajbhagat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Add-a-heading-480x251.png 480w, https://neerajbhagat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Add-a-heading-768x402.png 768w, https://neerajbhagat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Add-a-heading.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" />            </a>
